合征」为何会致死？在假期长途旅行和日常久坐中，我们如何预防这种疾病的发生？这个男女都爱的动作，是血管「杀手」！腿上出现 1 种变化，危险可能不远了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa660fdabbb8fd8dcd465572308ad986_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654368864"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7cGGvKKqkq1YEAMaCTEwNzY5MzA0MiCMj7exBjAAOBRAEnIJNjU0MzY4ODY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1714324552.22462", "card_id": "Q_652234883", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "跳槽离职前的最后一天，你会在工位上做什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-93a7e0342ad55cd92df86b6da27af0c2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652234883"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7cGGvKKqkq1YEAMaCTEwNzIxODU2MiCB9M6wBjAAOE5AE3IJNjUyMjM0ODgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1714324552.22686", "card_id": "Q_654380333", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "毕业后第一份工作，签劳动合同应该注意些什么？该怎么签才能避坑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "毕业季、就业潮，第一份工作总是令人印象深刻，你在签订第一份劳动合同时，遇到什么问题了吗？欢迎讨论~ 相关问题已收录至「法律观察室」话题活动，欢迎参与回答，抽奖赢好礼～法律观察室"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/65438